isEmpty

public static boolean isEmpty(java.util.List<?> sourceList)
判断list是否为空或大小为0

参数：
sourceList -
返回：
若list为null或长度为0, 返回true; 否则返回false. 
      isEmpty(null)   =   true;
      isEmpty({})     =   true;
      isEmpty({1})    =   false;

join

参数：

      join(null)      =   "";
      join({})        =   "";
      join({a,b})     =   "a,b";

join

                                    char separator)
将list中所有元素以separator分隔符拼接返回

参数：
list -
separator -
返回：
list中所有元素以separator分隔符拼接返回。若list为空或长度为0返回"" 
      join(null, "#")     =   "";
      join({}, "#")       =   "";
      join({a,b,c}, "")   =   "abc";
      join({a,b,c}, "#")  =   "a#b#c";

join

public static java.lang.String join(java.util.List<java.lang.String> list,
                                    java.lang.String separator)
将list中所有元素以separator分隔符拼接返回，separator为空则采用默认分隔符","

参数：
list -
separator -
返回：
list中所有元素以separator分隔符拼接返回。若list为空或长度为0返回"" 
      join(null, "#")     =   "";
      join({}, "#$")      =   "";
      join({a,b,c}, null) =   "a,b,c";
      join({a,b,c}, "")   =   "abc";
      join({a,b,c}, "#")  =   "a#b#c";
      join({a,b,c}, "#$") =   "a#$b#$c";

public static <V> boolean addListNotNullValue(java.util.List<V> sourceList,
                                              V value)
向list中新增value

参数：
sourceList -
value -
返回：
若add成功，返回true，否则返回false
  • 若sourceList为null，返回false
  • 若value为null，返回false
  • List.add(Object) 异常返回false
  • 以上皆不满足，返回true
